headline: DexCom Is Doubling Down on Its ‘Mistake.’ Why It’s Time to Buy the Stock.
summary: DexCom’s decision to pursue the Type 2 diabetes market wasn’t faulty. It was management’s execution of its strategy that caused the problem.
